{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/en/blog/2016-04-25-maiakovskiie-chtieniia/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"24th April 2016, Krasnoyarsk hosted the traditional (for the first time in five years, fuck!)\n“Mayakovsky Readings” dedicated to the poet…","fields":{"langKey":"en","slug":"/en/blog/2016-04-25-maiakovskiie-chtieniia/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"April 25, 2016","title":"Reading of Mayakovsky"},"html":"<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1280px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d8abe3dca3cdd97d921b04148f4ca697/eea4a/batya.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d8abe3dca3cdd97d921b04148f4ca697/d7c22/batya.avif 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/d8abe3dca3cdd97d921b04148f4ca697/af3f0/batya.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d8abe3dca3cdd97d921b04148f4ca697/eea4a/batya.jpg 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d8abe3dca3cdd97d921b04148f4ca697/eea4a/batya.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Father\"\n            title=\"Father\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Father</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>24th April 2016, Krasnoyarsk hosted the traditional (for the first time in five years, fuck!)\n“<a href=\"https://vk.com/mayakkrsk\">Mayakovsky Readings</a>” dedicated to the poet with the same\nname. There were few people because no one needed poetry. Most of all, the event was like a\ntet-a-tet for the philology and literary faculty of local universities. These people read awesome (I\ncouldn’t find pictures of a small lame man with a powerful voice):</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1280px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bdd0c239dec279f0e9ddeee8dea92b3c/eea4a/boroda.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/bdd0c239dec279f0e9ddeee8dea92b3c/d7c22/boroda.avif 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/bdd0c239dec279f0e9ddeee8dea92b3c/af3f0/boroda.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/bdd0c239dec279f0e9ddeee8dea92b3c/eea4a/boroda.jpg 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/bdd0c239dec279f0e9ddeee8dea92b3c/eea4a/boroda.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Beard\"\n            title=\"Beard\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Beard</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1280px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ef77f110692ff8d083d636eff1564560/eea4a/boroda2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ef77f110692ff8d083d636eff1564560/d7c22/boroda2.avif 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/ef77f110692ff8d083d636eff1564560/af3f0/boroda2.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ef77f110692ff8d083d636eff1564560/eea4a/boroda2.jpg 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ef77f110692ff8d083d636eff1564560/eea4a/boroda2.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Beard 2\"\n            title=\"Beard 2\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Beard 2</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1280px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f86904c77b33e03d6f860a7a12ed5ecc/eea4a/cvetkov.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f86904c77b33e03d6f860a7a12ed5ecc/d7c22/cvetkov.avif 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/f86904c77b33e03d6f860a7a12ed5ecc/af3f0/cvetkov.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f86904c77b33e03d6f860a7a12ed5ecc/eea4a/cvetkov.jpg 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f86904c77b33e03d6f860a7a12ed5ecc/eea4a/cvetkov.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Cvetkov\"\n            title=\"Cvetkov\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Cvetkov</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4a738ce29af65b56a2f7aceeaace9bfe/212bf/nefediev.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/4a738ce29af65b56a2f7aceeaace9bfe/0bbb0/nefediev.avif 768w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/4a738ce29af65b56a2f7aceeaace9bfe/8b983/nefediev.webp 768w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/4a738ce29af65b56a2f7aceeaace9bfe/212bf/nefediev.jpg 768w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/4a738ce29af65b56a2f7aceeaace9bfe/212bf/nefediev.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Nefed’ev\"\n            title=\"Nefed’ev\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Nefed’ev</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>I don’t presume to judge her, so as not to be biased (it is worth noting that at least she was\naudible, unlike other women, who generally muttered something in a half-whisper under their breath):</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1239px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/45ea1d43e1324df315a21669004ad41d/16baf/sergienko.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.64729620661824%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/45ea1d43e1324df315a21669004ad41d/469ef/sergienko.avif 1239w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1239px) 100vw, 1239px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/45ea1d43e1324df315a21669004ad41d/62b6b/sergienko.webp 1239w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1239px) 100vw, 1239px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/45ea1d43e1324df315a21669004ad41d/16baf/sergienko.jpg 1239w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1239px) 100vw, 1239px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/45ea1d43e1324df315a21669004ad41d/16baf/sergienko.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Sergienko\"\n            title=\"Sergienko\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Sergienko</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>The rest read like shit. The most interesting thing is that they were absolutely not ashamed of\ntheir reading… I was ashamed (vicarious embarrassment in all its glory, yes!). Periodically, a drunk\nwith two dogs on one leash amused the crowd (at the bottom left, you can even see a “piece” of a\ndog):</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1280px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d4f35058fd7b6dea90a582b81556621b/eea4a/alkash.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d4f35058fd7b6dea90a582b81556621b/d7c22/alkash.avif 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/d4f35058fd7b6dea90a582b81556621b/af3f0/alkash.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d4f35058fd7b6dea90a582b81556621b/eea4a/alkash.jpg 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d4f35058fd7b6dea90a582b81556621b/eea4a/alkash.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Drunk\"\n            title=\"Drunk\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Drunk</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>But the highlight of the program was a casual (although I doubt) passer-by whom I called “dad”. He,\nlike a tornado, ran into the circle of spectators and readers, said some words, and began to shout\npoetry. He yelled them extremely awesome: with anguish in his voice, flying saliva, a burning\neye-to-eye sight of his “victims”, with a bottle of some sort of drink in his hand (or not, I didn’t\nremember, because I was fucked from a sudden and abrupt reading!), some gesticulation (sometimes\neven “attacking”). Having shouted “verse”, he was about to leave and shout to us all “I’ll go drink\nfurther!” But then he came back and gave us more poetry. It was worth attending these readings only\nfor his sake. Just for his sake. Only. For. His. Sake. Very cool!</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1280px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d8abe3dca3cdd97d921b04148f4ca697/eea4a/batya.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d8abe3dca3cdd97d921b04148f4ca697/d7c22/batya.avif 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/d8abe3dca3cdd97d921b04148f4ca697/af3f0/batya.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d8abe3dca3cdd97d921b04148f4ca697/eea4a/batya.jpg 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d8abe3dca3cdd97d921b04148f4ca697/eea4a/batya.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Dad\"\n            title=\"Dad\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Dad</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Readings were ended with obscene verses about “love is like a piece of pussy”, “dick from mouth to\nmouth” and political about “It’s Putin’s fault.” The readings were definitely successful. We’ll have\nto go some more.</p>","id":"20dc8069-504e-5aa2-806e-1bea17002f3e"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ITFarrier"}}},"pageContext":{"langKey":"en","language":"en","next":{"fields":{"langKey":"en","slug":"/en/blog/2016-05-11-donorstvo/"},"frontmatter":{"language":null,"title":"Donation","type":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"langKey":"en","slug":"/en/blog/2016-04-17-novyi-dizain-vkontaktie/"},"frontmatter":{"language":null,"title":"New design of VK","type":null}},"slug":"/en/blog/2016-04-25-maiakovskiie-chtieniia/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2448238595","3823719399"]}